title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Start from scratch - Boeing 787
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can start the Boeing 787 from scratch including programming the MCDU.
We programmed the flight using the build-in flightplanner from MSFS 2020 since no Simbrief integration is available for this aircraft.
